<h2>Scope and Usage</h2>
<p>
The ProcessResponse resource indicates the resource for which the processing status is requested and 
provides simple acknowledgement and status information of application level errors. It may also be used to 
convey additional processing requirements in a text form.
</p>
<p>
This is the formal response to a ProcessRequest and may be used as a application level response to PaymentNotice 
and SupportingDocumentation resources.
</p>
